description: Demolition of all existing buildings including vehicle repair garage in Spanish road and terraced houses in Northside Wandsworth Common. Erection of a part five, part six-storey building containing ground floor commercial floorspace A2, A3, B1, D1 or sui generis uses, 67 private residential flats and 29 affordable flats. Erection of three-storey plus basement building fronting Spanish Road for 12 private flats. 27 surface level car parking spaces, a ramp to 43 basement car parking spaces, bin and cycle stores. Provision of a road to provide potential future road link between East Hill and Northside Wandsworth Common.
